{"tid":929331,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無啲長期病痛係啲奇難雜症，睇極醫生都醫唔好？","createTime":"2018-12-05T13:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T13:33:54.000Z","uid":225353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea4391c08ecd8dab16bb12ea00ca6de66f10895f","tid":929331,"uid":225353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:12:53.000Z","msg":"有名有目嘅病就梗係無問題，但如何係啲怪症又睇極醫生都唔知咩事影響到生活就真係愁，希望大家分享一下自己嘅怪症，睇吓各巴絲有無遇過同點解決？"},{"pid":"981d7e957cdc2c34a381dd9bbbab6ae6749caf92","tid":929331,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"偏頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a9a9217cd481de9883e95f36112df86c322ea5","tid":929331,"uid":225353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"包皮痛咗足足差唔多四個月，皮膚科醫生定泌尿科醫生檢查過晒都冇明顯病徵，亦都抽過血驗過小便同精液內裏亦無再發現細菌，但係包皮嘅痛楚依然持續，我已經食咗無數咁多抗生素、消炎止痛藥依然冇好轉，包皮表面完全冇紅無腫冇發炎，但就keep住痛，而家都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682ce4859878ed529edc46883036b0ab869bcf65","tid":929331,"uid":225353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"981d7e957cdc2c34a381dd9bbbab6ae6749caf92","tid":929331,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"偏頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:19:35.000Z","msg":"咁你點解決？影響日常生活嗎？"},{"pid":"49de4b3f8f04d96409238c6f87b2963e98a40b03","tid":929331,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"窮"},{"pid":"60fdaa0c7740bd5c308c12a1579306f05523ef24","tid":929331,"uid":71140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0cd4f997f672351a397fbe9d53a9906d5cf892a","tid":929331,"uid":225353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60fdaa0c7740bd5c308c12a1579306f05523ef24","tid":929331,"uid":71140,"like"